  <data key="d0">"ORGANISM"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Bee is an insect capable of digesting a certain amount of sugar in its lifetime."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bee is an organism capable of digesting a certain amount of sugar in its lifetime, and its lifespan is influenced by the active or off season of the colony."</data>
