</node>
<node id="&quot;ACTIVE SEASON&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Active season is a period when bees are more industrious and engaged in their tasks."&lt;SEP&gt;"Active season is a period when bees are working harder, leading to a shorter lifespan."&lt;SEP&gt;"Active season refers to the period when beekeeping activities are most intense, typically involving regular visits to the hives."</data>
