<node id="&quot;OFF SEASON&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"TIME_PERIOD"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Off season is a period when bees are idle and eat less, leading to a longer lifespan."&lt;SEP&gt;"Off season is a period when bees are less active and engaged in fewer tasks."</data>
