</node>
<node id="&quot;WORKERS'&lt; COMPENSATION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"BENEFIT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Workers' compensation is a type of insurance providing protection to employees injured in the course of employment."&lt;SEP&gt;"Workers' compensation is a type of insurance providing wage replacement and medical benefits to employees injured in the course of employment."&lt;SEP&gt;"Workers' compensation is a type of insurance providing wage replacement to employees injured in the course of employment."</data>
