</node>
<node id="&quot;BROOD&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Brood refers to the developing bees within the hive, which also give off pheromones signaling the status and needs of the hive."&lt;SEP&gt;"Brood refers to the developing offspring of bees, which can influence the development phases of young bees within the colony."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-5432dc0f860913abcd37f8b24e3bcc22&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a5a56afe52a888e5c4267f47f027e036</data>
