<node id="&quot;POLLEN FORAGERS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Pollen foragers are a subgroup of foraging bees that collect pollen from flowers and bring it back to the hive."&lt;SEP&gt;"Pollen foragers are bees that collect pollen and inadvertently bring back insecticides to the hive, affecting the young bees."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-5432dc0f860913abcd37f8b24e3bcc22&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a5a56afe52a888e5c4267f47f027e036</data>
