</node>
<node id="&quot;NURSE BEES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANISM"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Nurse bees are young bees that care for the brood, and their development can be affected by the presence of insecticides in the hive."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-5432dc0f860913abcd37f8b24e3bcc22</data>
