<node id="&quot;HONEY BEE COLONY&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Honey Bee Colony is a social insect structure where bees live and work together, maintaining a year-round activity pattern."&lt;SEP&gt;"Honey bee colony is the main subject of discussion, referring to the group of bees that live, work, and reproduce together."</data>
