<node id="&quot;RELATIVE INACTIVITY&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Relative Inactivity describes the periods within the honey bee colony where activity is lower but not completely halted."&lt;SEP&gt;"Relative inactivity is a period during the year when the hive's activity levels decrease but do not completely cease."</data>
