</node>
<node id="&quot;SUMMER&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Summer is a period of high activity and population in the honey bee colony, with abundant forage available."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-a40a756fcfe048bdd7aa9b2b44a0469e</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 13}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 78}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;FALL&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Fall is a transitional period where the honey bee colony starts preparing for winter, reducing population and activity levels."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-a40a756fcfe048bdd7aa9b2b44a0469e</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 13}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 78}]</data>
