<node id="&quot;MONEY&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Money is a factor considered by beekeepers, both as a side benefit of a hobby and as a potential primary goal for more experienced beekeepers."&lt;SEP&gt;"Money refers to the financial aspect of beekeeping, where the primary goal is to make a profit, but it often involves initial costs and uncertainties."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-d4ff0d3047b19e50793ea40860c34e98&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-25b63504237ee11d327b37a8abd236b3</data>
