  <data key="d1">"Right of First Refusal is a contractual right that allows the Company or its Subsidiaries to purchase a product or service before others."&lt;SEP&gt;"Right of first refusal is a legal right that allows a party to match any offer made to another party, ensuring priority in purchasing or licensing opportunities."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-aabc464002a4ba146a5fb5107b31b72c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d4ff0d3047b19e50793ea40860c34e98</data>
