  <data key="d1">"Option to Purchase is a contractual right that allows the Company or its Subsidiaries to buy a product or service at a later date."&lt;SEP&gt;"Option to purchase is a legal right that gives a party the ability to buy a product or service at a predetermined price within a specified time frame."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-aabc464002a4ba146a5fb5107b31b72c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d4ff0d3047b19e50793ea40860c34e98</data>
