<node id="&quot;ECOSYSTEMS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Ecosystems are complex networks of living organisms and their physical environment, which are affected by human activities and the Serengeti Rules."&lt;SEP&gt;"Ecosystems refer to complex biological communities and their physical environment, which can become 'sick' when the populations of certain species are imbalanced."&lt;SEP&gt;"Ecosystems refer to complex systems of living organisms and their physical environment, which can be 'sick' due to imbalances in population dynamics."</data>
