<node id="&quot;CANNON&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Cannon is a medical doctor who is part of the crew and later works in various field hospitals, dealing with casualties from a major British offensive."&lt;SEP&gt;"Cannon is a medical researcher who conducted experiments on shock patients and discovered the relationship between bicarbonate levels and blood pressure."&lt;SEP&gt;"Cannon is a physiologist who chaired a special committee to advise the government on ways to protect lives in wartime, focusing on battlefield medicine."&lt;SEP&gt;"Cannon is a physiologist who chaired a special committee to advise the government on ways to protect the lives of soldiers and civilians during wartime, focusing on battlefield medicine."&lt;SEP&gt;"Cannon is a physiologist who recognized shock symptoms in wounded soldiers and conducted experiments to understand and mitigate the syndrome."&lt;SEP&gt;"Cannon is the author of a book discussing the 'wisdom of the body' and the logic behind life's processes."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-f57af36635a6b8ade4cbaf6b9d73c825&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e565e66ef834e4caca689e27371f4bd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9e5759c1eccdacad5abbaa5faf9975ba&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b6913df09c658e382a60bc398c049d7f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6a1794c4fa3680656aaab5d3de43949e</data>
