  <data key="d0">"TIME PERIOD"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The 1960s is a decade when significant changes in vocal production techniques occurred in musical performances."&lt;SEP&gt;"The 1960s marked a significant turning point in vocal production with the introduction of the pop/rock musical form, reflecting social changes in America."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-0267286c81e05982bbb46c95364cbb30&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bb2da1f90d8529348f68db024bb17056</data>
