  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The 1968 production of Hair was a pivotal moment in musical theater, using rock genre and electric instruments, leading to the amplification of singing voices."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-0267286c81e05982bbb46c95364cbb30</data>
