  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Text understanding and communication is the primary goal of vocal production in music theater, emphasizing clarity and emotional expression."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-59e10c7e6d1073196e6649875ab91569</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;ROCK MUSICALS OF THE 1960S&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Rock musicals of the 1960s addressed topical political and social issues, reflecting the cultural and societal changes of that era."&lt;SEP&gt;"Rock musicals of the 1960s were a genre of musical theater that addressed topical political and social issues of the era, often featuring mix/belt vocal production."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-59e10c7e6d1073196e6649875ab91569&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5e1db9c56d4738764f06ecc0b5763c66</data>
