  <data key="d2">chunk-5e1db9c56d4738764f06ecc0b5763c66</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;MIX/BELT SINGING&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Mix/belt singing is a vocal technique that females are taking up to E5 and beyond, suggesting a progression in skill level."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-5e1db9c56d4738764f06ecc0b5763c66</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;EQUAL RIGHTS MOVEMENT&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The Equal Rights Movement was a significant social change during the 1960s, advocating for gender equality and changing traditional gender roles."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-5e1db9c56d4738764f06ecc0b5763c66</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;SHIFTING GENDER ROLES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
