  <data key="d2">chunk-5e1db9c56d4738764f06ecc0b5763c66</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;1960S MUSICALS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"1960s Musical plays reflected the social and political changes of the time, including the creation of female and male characters with similar vocal ranges."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-5e1db9c56d4738764f06ecc0b5763c66</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;VOCAL SYSTEM&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Vocal System includes the power source (breath), the vibrator (vocal folds), and the resonator (vocal tract), which work together to produce the singing voice."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-5e1db9c56d4738764f06ecc0b5763c66</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 19}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 99}]</data>
