</node>
<node id="&quot;ROUND DANCE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Round Dance is a type of dance performed by foragers to indicate the location of food sources within 100 meters of the hive."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Round Dance is a specific type of dance performed by bees to signal the discovery of a new source of nectar or pollen within 100 meters of the hive. It conveys that the source is within a 100-meter radius but does not provide further details."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-53ba801aab88a318b172032db00d5a26&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9e973cd1cc5f8803251af14f60c371c6</data>
