</node>
<node id="&quot;MUTATION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Mutations in oncogenes, including the bcr/abl fusion, lead to the development of various cancers, highlighting the role of genetic alterations in cancer."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-6a1794c4fa3680656aaab5d3de43949e</data>
</node>
