  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Impact and Friction refer to the forces experienced by the vocal folds during use."&lt;SEP&gt;"Impact and Friction refer to the physical forces exerted on the vocal folds during singing, which can lead to fatigue and strain if not properly managed."</data>
