  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Adequate Oral Hydration Recommendations are guidelines for maintaining proper hydration levels to prevent the mucus from becoming thick and sticky."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-48744b276bffa8148a6398e5afebc9e2</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 16}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 82}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;CAFFEINE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Caffeine is a substance that can potentially dry the membranes and should be minimized to maintain proper hydration."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-48744b276bffa8148a6398e5afebc9e2</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 16}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 82}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;MEDICATIONS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Medications are substances that can potentially dry the membranes and should be minimized to maintain proper hydration."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-48744b276bffa8148a6398e5afebc9e2</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 16}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 82}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;DRY AIR&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Dry Air is an environmental factor that can contribute to dehydration and should be minimized to maintain proper hydration."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-48744b276bffa8148a6398e5afebc9e2</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 16}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 82}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;MUCUS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Mucus is produced by the body at a rate of approximately two quarts per day and can become thick and sticky if not adequately hydrated."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-48744b276bffa8148a6398e5afebc9e2</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 16}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 82}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;PHONOTRAUMA&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Phonotrauma includes vocal behaviors such as yelling, screaming, loud talking, harsh sneezing, and harsh laughing that can compromise the integrity of the vibration patterns of the vocal folds."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-48744b276bffa8148a6398e5afebc9e2</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 16}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 83}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 141}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;MALE SPEAKING FREQUENCY&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The average fundamental speaking frequency for males ranges from 100 to 150 Hz."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-48744b276bffa8148a6398e5afebc9e2</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 16}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 83}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 141}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;FEMALE SPEAKING FREQUENCY&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The average fundamental speaking frequency for females ranges from 180 to 230 Hz."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-48744b276bffa8148a6398e5afebc9e2</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 16}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 83}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 141}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;VOCAL BEHAVIORS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Vocal Behaviors refer to actions that can compromise the integrity of the vocal folds, including phonotraumatic behaviors such as yelling and screaming."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-48744b276bffa8148a6398e5afebc9e2</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 16}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 83}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 141}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;PHONOTRAUMATIC BEHAVIORS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Phonotraumatic Behaviors are vocal actions that can cause damage to the vocal folds, including yelling, screaming, loud talking, harsh sneezing, and harsh laughing."&lt;SEP&gt;"Phonotraumatic behaviors refer to actions such as yelling, screaming, loud talking, harsh sneezing, and harsh laughing that can cause damage to the vocal folds."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-48744b276bffa8148a6398e5afebc9e2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f048b0415055a67eb6c616d2e3dadcb3</data>
