  <data key="d4">89.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Company and Subsidiaries are part of the same corporate structure, and notices or proceedings could affect both."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company and its Subsidiaries are related through ownership and operational affiliations."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subsidiaries are affiliated with the Company and could be affected by notices or proceedings related to the Transactions."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company and its Subsidiaries are conducting their business and operations in compliance with various laws and regulations."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company and its Subsidiaries operate in countries affected by SARS-CoV-2 and COVID-19, facing similar challenges."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company has Subsidiaries that can enter into various types of contracts and agreements."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company oversees its Subsidiaries and ensures compliance with environmental laws."</data>
