<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;DEBTOR&quot;">
  <data key="d4">40.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Company has obligations towards the Debtor under the agreement, and the Debtor has rights that are unaffected by the agreement."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Debtor can enforce any right, remedy, condition, consent, or approval requirement under the agreement or any Definitive Document without conflicting with the Company's obligations."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Debtor can take or direct actions relating to the maintenance, protection, or preservation of itself without conflicting with the Company's obligations."</data>
