  <data key="d4">84.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Chores, such as opening the hive, can present challenges in colony management."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-25b63504237ee11d327b37a8abd236b3</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;CHORE&quot;" target="&quot;RESPONSIBILITIES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">84.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Chores, such as opening the hive, are part of the responsibilities of beekeepers."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-25b63504237ee11d327b37a8abd236b3</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;CHORE&quot;" target="&quot;ACTIVITIES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">84.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Chores, such as opening the hive, are part of the various activities performed by beekeepers."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-25b63504237ee11d327b37a8abd236b3</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;FIRST YEAR&quot;" target="&quot;INTENSITY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The intensity of effort required in beekeeping increases over time, especially during the first year."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-25b63504237ee11d327b37a8abd236b3</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;INTENSITY&quot;" target="&quot;VOICE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Voice involves controlling Intensity to adjust the volume or loudness of the sound."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-48744b276bffa8148a6398e5afebc9e2</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SURPLUS HONEY&quot;" target="&quot;SIDELINE BUSINESS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">14.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Surplus honey can potentially contribute to a sideline business if produced in sufficient quantities after covering initial costs."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-d4ff0d3047b19e50793ea40860c34e98</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SURPLUS HONEY&quot;" target="&quot;INITIAL COSTS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Initial costs are covered by surplus honey sales, which can occur after a couple of years of beekeeping."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-d4ff0d3047b19e50793ea40860c34e98</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;CROP POLLINATION&quot;" target="&quot;SIDELINE BUSINESS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">12.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Crop pollination can be a part of a sideline business if beekeeping is pursued as a hobby and becomes profitable."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-d4ff0d3047b19e50793ea40860c34e98</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;PRODUCT&quot;" target="&quot;RIGHT OF FIRST REFUSAL&quot;">
  <data key="d4">27.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A right of first refusal can be granted with respect to a Product, allowing a party to match any offer made to another party."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-d4ff0d3047b19e50793ea40860c34e98</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;PRODUCT&quot;" target="&quot;OPTION TO PURCHASE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">24.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"An option to purchase can be granted with respect to a Product, giving a party the ability to buy the product at a predetermined price within a specified time frame."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-d4ff0d3047b19e50793ea40860c34e98</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;PRODUCT&quot;" target="&quot;OPTION TO LICENSE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">21.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"An option to license can be granted with respect to a Product, allowing a party to negotiate the terms of a license agreement for the product."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-d4ff0d3047b19e50793ea40860c34e98</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARY&quot;" target="&quot;PERSON&quot;">
  <data key="d4">9.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A Person can own or control a Subsidiary, as defined by the ownership or control of a majority of the voting power."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-78efcb7cc86e646cd522e63d35449266</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;VARIABLES AND PROBLEMS&quot;" target="&quot;INITIAL COSTS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Variables and problems affect the initial costs of beekeeping, making it challenging to predict financial outcomes."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-d4ff0d3047b19e50793ea40860c34e98</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;EXPERIENCED BEEKEEPER&quot;" target="&quot;NEW BEEKEEPER&quot;">
  <data key="d4">6.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Experienced beekeepers may consider making money from beekeeping, but it is not a guarantee, unlike new beekeepers who are more likely to engage in it as a hobby."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-d4ff0d3047b19e50793ea40860c34e98</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
