  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Physiologist is the professional role held by Cannon, focusing on the study of bodily functions and processes."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-f57af36635a6b8ade4cbaf6b9d73c825</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;CANNON&quot;" target="&quot;EXPERIMENTAL STUDIES OF ANIMALS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">9.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Experimental studies of animals refers to Cannon's research on animals under stress to understand shock symptoms."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-f57af36635a6b8ade4cbaf6b9d73c825</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;CANNON&quot;" target="&quot;EXPERIMENTAL STUDIES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Experimental studies are scientific investigations conducted by Cannon to understand shock symptoms in animals."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-f57af36635a6b8ade4cbaf6b9d73c825</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;CANNON&quot;" target="&quot;WOUNDED SOLDIERS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Wounded soldiers are the subjects of Cannon's observations and experiments, who exhibit shock symptoms such as rapid pulse and heavy sweating."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-f57af36635a6b8ade4cbaf6b9d73c825</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;CANNON&quot;" target="&quot;SOLDIERS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Cannon studied the blood pressure of soldiers to understand normal and abnormal ranges, which informed his research on shock patients."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-b6913df09c658e382a60bc398c049d7f</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
