  <data key="d4">130.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Debtors are engaging with Supporting Lenders in a credit agreement."&lt;SEP&gt;"Debtors are involved in agreements with the Supporting Lenders."&lt;SEP&gt;"Debtors must consult weekly with the Supporting Lenders' legal counsel and financial advisor regarding strategic planning and negotiations."&lt;SEP&gt;"Debtors must consult with Supporting Lenders' legal counsel and financial advisor regarding strategic planning and negotiations."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are involved in agreements with the Debtors."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders must ensure that the Debtors comply with the DIP Orders and Restructuring process."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders must provide legal and financial advice to the Debtors."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders provide support and guidance to the Debtors in the restructuring process."</data>
