<edge source="&quot;TAKEOVER STATUTE&quot;" target="&quot;FAIR PRICE LAW&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Fair Price Law is part of the broader Takeover Statute, aimed at ensuring fair pricing during takeovers."</data>
