  <data key="d4">9.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Takeover Statute is a specific example of Anti-Takeover Law, which includes provisions for 'fair price,' 'moratorium,' and 'control share acquisition.'"</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;INCOME TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX RETURN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A Tax Return includes information about Income Tax, which is a type of tax levied on the income earned by individuals or organizations."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
