  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Income Tax is a type of Tax levied on the income earned by individuals or organizations."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;FRANCHISE TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX RETURN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A Tax Return includes information about Franchise Tax, which is a tax levied on corporations based on their existence or privilege to do business."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;FRANCHISE TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Franchise Tax is a type of Tax levied on corporations based on their existence or privilege to do business."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;WINDFALL PROFITS TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX RETURN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A Tax Return includes information about Windfall Profits Tax, which is a temporary tax levied on extraordinary profits, often during times of economic crisis."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;WINDFALL PROFITS TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Windfall Profits Tax is a type of Tax levied on extraordinary profits, often during times of economic crisis."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;GROSS RECEIPTS TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX RETURN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A Tax Return includes information about Gross Receipts Tax, which is a tax levied on the total revenue generated by a business before expenses."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
