  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Gross Receipts Tax is a type of Tax levied on the total revenue generated by a business before expenses."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;PROPERTY TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX RETURN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A Tax Return includes information about Property Tax, which is a tax levied on real estate based on its value."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
