  <data key="d5">"A Tax Return includes information about Sales Tax, which is a tax levied on the sale of goods and services."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SALES TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Sales Tax is a type of Tax levied on the sale of goods and services."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;USE TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX RETURN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A Tax Return includes information about Use Tax, which is a tax levied on the use of tangible personal property that has not been subject to sales tax."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;USE TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Use Tax is a type of Tax levied on the use of tangible personal property that has not been subject to sales tax."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;NET WORTH TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX RETURN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A Tax Return includes information about Net Worth Tax, which is a tax levied on the total assets minus liabilities of an individual or organization."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;NET WORTH TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Net Worth Tax is a type of Tax levied on the total assets minus liabilities of an individual or organization."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;CAPITAL STOCK TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX RETURN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A Tax Return includes information about Capital Stock Tax, which is a tax levied on the ownership of stock in a corporation."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;CAPITAL STOCK TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Capital Stock Tax is a type of Tax levied on the ownership of stock in a corporation."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;PAYROLL TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX RETURN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A Tax Return includes information about Payroll Tax, which is a tax levied on the wages paid to employees."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;PAYROLL TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Payroll Tax is a type of Tax levied on the wages paid to employees."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;EMPLOYMENT TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX RETURN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A Tax Return includes information about Employment Tax, which is a tax levied on the hiring of employees, often including social security and Medicare taxes."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;EMPLOYMENT TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Employment Tax is a type of Tax levied on the hiring of employees, often including social security and Medicare taxes."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SOCIAL SECURITY TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX RETURN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A Tax Return includes information about Social Security Tax, which is a tax levied on both employers and employees to fund social security programs."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SOCIAL SECURITY TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Social Security Tax is a type of Tax levied on both employers and employees to fund social security programs."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;WORKERS' COMPENSATION TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX RETURN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A Tax Return includes information about Workers' Compensation Tax, which is a tax levied on employers to fund workers' compensation programs."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;WORKERS' COMPENSATION TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Workers' Compensation Tax is a type of Tax levied on employers to fund workers' compensation programs."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;UNEMPLOYMENT COMPENSATION TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX RETURN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A Tax Return includes information about Unemployment Compensation Tax, which is a tax levied on employers to fund unemployment insurance programs."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;UNEMPLOYMENT COMPENSATION TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Unemployment Compensation Tax is a type of Tax levied on employers to fund unemployment insurance programs."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;EXCISE TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX RETURN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A Tax Return includes information about Excise Tax, which is a tax levied on specific goods or services, such as gasoline or tobacco."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;EXCISE TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Excise Tax is a type of Tax levied on specific goods or services, such as gasoline or tobacco."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;WITHHOLDING TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX RETURN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A Tax Return includes information about Withholding Tax, which is a tax levied on the payment of income to individuals, typically withheld by the payer."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;WITHHOLDING TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Withholding Tax is a type of Tax levied on the payment of income to individuals, typically withheld by the payer."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;AD VALOREM TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX RETURN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A Tax Return includes information about Ad Valorem Tax, which is a tax levied on the assessed value of property."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;AD VALOREM TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Ad Valorem Tax is a type of Tax levied on the assessed value of property."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;STAMP TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX RETURN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A Tax Return includes information about Stamp Tax, which is a tax levied on the execution, delivery, or transfer of documents."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;STAMP TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Stamp Tax is a type of Tax levied on the execution, delivery, or transfer of documents."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;TRANSFER TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX RETURN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A Tax Return includes information about Transfer Tax, which is a tax levied on the transfer of property, such as real estate."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;TRANSFER TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Transfer Tax is a type of Tax levied on the transfer of property, such as real estate."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;VALUE-ADDED TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX RETURN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A Tax Return includes information about Value-Added Tax, which is a tax levied on the value added at each stage of production and distribution."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;VALUE-ADDED TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Value-Added Tax is a type of Tax levied on the value added at each stage of production and distribution."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;OCCUPATION TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX RETURN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A Tax Return includes information about Occupation Tax, which is a tax levied on the right to engage in a particular occupation or profession."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;OCCUPATION TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Occupation Tax is a type of Tax levied on the right to engage in a particular occupation or profession."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;ENVIRONMENTAL TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX RETURN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A Tax Return includes information about Environmental Tax, which is a tax levied on activities that cause environmental harm."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;ENVIRONMENTAL TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Environmental Tax is a type of Tax levied on activities that cause environmental harm."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;DISABILITY TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX RETURN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A Tax Return includes information about Disability Tax, which is a tax levied on employers to fund disability programs."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;DISABILITY TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Disability Tax is a type of Tax levied on employers to fund disability programs."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;REAL PROPERTY TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX RETURN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A Tax Return includes information about Real Property Tax, which is a tax levied on real estate based on its value."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;REAL PROPERTY TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Real Property Tax is a type of Tax levied on real estate based on its value."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;PERSONAL PROPERTY TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX RETURN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A Tax Return includes information about Personal Property Tax, which is a tax levied on tangible personal property, such as vehicles or equipment."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;PERSONAL PROPERTY TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Personal Property Tax is a type of Tax levied on tangible personal property, such as vehicles or equipment."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;REGISTRATION TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX RETURN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A Tax Return includes information about Registration Tax, which is a tax levied on the registration of property or other assets."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;REGISTRATION TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Registration Tax is a type of Tax levied on the registration of property or other assets."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;ALTERNATIVE MINIMUM TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX RETURN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A Tax Return includes information about Alternative Minimum Tax, which is a tax levied to ensure that high-income individuals pay a minimum level of tax."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;ALTERNATIVE MINIMUM TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Alternative Minimum Tax is a type of Tax levied to ensure that high-income individuals pay a minimum level of tax."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;ADD-ON MINIMUM TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX RETURN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A Tax Return includes information about Add-On Minimum Tax, which is a tax levied to ensure that high-income individuals pay a minimum level of tax, often added to the regular tax."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;ADD-ON MINIMUM TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Add-On Minimum Tax is a type of Tax levied to ensure that high-income individuals pay a minimum level of tax, often added to the regular tax."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;ESTIMATED TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX RETURN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A Tax Return includes information about Estimated Tax, which is a tax levied on the estimated annual tax liability of individuals or organizations."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;ESTIMATED TAX&quot;" target="&quot;TAX&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Estimated Tax is a type of Tax levied on the estimated annual tax liability of individuals or organizations."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;ANTI-TAKEOVER LAW&quot;" target="&quot;U.S. FEDERAL GOVERNMENT&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"U.S. Federal Government enforces federal Anti-Takeover Laws, which include provisions for 'fair price,' 'moratorium,' and 'control share acquisition.'"</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;ANTI-TAKEOVER LAW&quot;" target="&quot;STATE GOVERNMENT&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"State Government enforces state-level Anti-Takeover Laws, which include provisions for 'fair price,' 'moratorium,' and 'control share acquisition.'"</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;ANTI-TAKEOVER LAW&quot;" target="&quot;LOCAL GOVERNMENT&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Local Government enforces local Anti-Takeover Laws, which include provisions for 'fair price,' 'moratorium,' and 'control share acquisition.'"</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;ANTI-TAKEOVER LAW&quot;" target="&quot;NON-U.S. GOVERNMENT&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Non-U.S. Government enforces international Anti-Takeover Laws, which include provisions for 'fair price,' 'moratorium,' and 'control share acquisition.'"</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4f5291955ed514f3c0e0eb381e9616fe</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;U.S. FEDERAL GOVERNMENT&quot;" target="&quot;TAX RETURN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Tax Returns may be filed with the U.S. Federal Government."|&lt;SEP&gt;"U.S. Federal Government is a part of the Taxing Authority that receives Tax Returns."|</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-2c97437b365f5eb5e2f2cc5e0ff5a3ec</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;STATE GOVERNMENT&quot;" target="&quot;TAX RETURN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"State Government is a part of the Taxing Authority that receives Tax Returns."|&lt;SEP&gt;"Tax Returns may be filed with State Governments."|</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-2c97437b365f5eb5e2f2cc5e0ff5a3ec</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;LOCAL GOVERNMENT&quot;" target="&quot;TAX RETURN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Local Government is a part of the Taxing Authority that receives Tax Returns."|&lt;SEP&gt;"Tax Returns may be filed with Local Governments."|</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-2c97437b365f5eb5e2f2cc5e0ff5a3ec</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;TAX RETURN&quot;" target="&quot;TAXING AUTHORITY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">24.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Tax Returns are filed with Taxing Authorities in connection with the determination, assessment, or collection of any Tax."|&lt;SEP&gt;"Tax Returns are filed with Taxing Authorities."|&lt;SEP&gt;"Taxing Authorities are the entities that receive Tax Returns."|</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-2c97437b365f5eb5e2f2cc5e0ff5a3ec</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;TAX RETURN&quot;" target="&quot;TAX&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Tax Returns are filed in connection with the determination, assessment, or collection of any Tax."|</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-2c97437b365f5eb5e2f2cc5e0ff5a3ec</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;TAX RETURN&quot;" target="&quot;LAWS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Tax Returns are filed in connection with the administration of any laws, regulations, or administrative requirements relating to any Tax."|</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-2c97437b365f5eb5e2f2cc5e0ff5a3ec</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;TAX RETURN&quot;" target="&quot;REGULATORY AUTHORITY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">24.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Regulatory Authority is the entity that enforces Tax Returns."|&lt;SEP&gt;"Tax Returns are filed with Taxing Authorities, which exercise regulatory authority in respect of taxes."|&lt;SEP&gt;"Tax Returns are subject to the enforcement of Regulatory Authorities."|</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-2c97437b365f5eb5e2f2cc5e0ff5a3ec</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;TAX RETURN&quot;" target="&quot;GOODWILL&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Tax Returns are filed in connection with the determination, assessment, or collection of any Tax, which may involve the administration of goodwill."|</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-2c97437b365f5eb5e2f2cc5e0ff5a3ec</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
