<edge source="&quot;AFRICANIZED BEES&quot;" target="&quot;STATE OR PROVINCE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The presence of Africanized bees affects the legality of picking up and hiving swarms in certain states or provinces."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-817bec40e1f316234277157c4faca623</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;STATE OR PROVINCE&quot;" target="&quot;SWARMS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">14.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"State or province regulations affect the handling of swarms due to the presence of Africanized bees."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-817bec40e1f316234277157c4faca623</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;WILD COLONY&quot;" target="&quot;HOLLOW TREES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">14.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Wild colonies can be found in hollow trees, which are natural nesting sites for bees."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-817bec40e1f316234277157c4faca623</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;WILD COLONY&quot;" target="&quot;CHIMNEYS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">14.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Wild colonies can be found in chimneys, which are artificial nesting sites for bees."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-817bec40e1f316234277157c4faca623</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;WILD COLONY&quot;" target="&quot;WALLS OF A BUILDING&quot;">
  <data key="d4">14.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Wild colonies can be found in the walls of buildings, which are enclosed and often inaccessible."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-817bec40e1f316234277157c4faca623</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEEKEEPING PUBLICATIONS&quot;" target="&quot;NUCLEUS HIVES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">18.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Beekeeping Publications advertise nucleus hives, providing information on where to find them."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-c0a8c416dc0695d5c1e06f3541ce9ffc</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEEKEEPING EQUIPMENT SUPPLIER&quot;" target="&quot;NUCLEUS HIVES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Beekeeping Equipment Suppliers provide information on where to get nucleus hives."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-c0a8c416dc0695d5c1e06f3541ce9ffc</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;LOCAL BEEKEEPING PUBLICATIONS&quot;" target="&quot;NUCLEUS HIVES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">14.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Local Beekeeping Publications provide additional information on nucleus hives."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-c0a8c416dc0695d5c1e06f3541ce9ffc</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMMERCIAL BEEKEEPERS&quot;" target="&quot;NUCLEUS HIVES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">18.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Commercial Beekeepers produce nucleus hives, often locally."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-c0a8c416dc0695d5c1e06f3541ce9ffc</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SIDELINE BEEKEEPERS&quot;" target="&quot;NUCLEUS HIVES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Sideline Beekeepers also produce nucleus hives, sometimes with extra bees."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-c0a8c416dc0695d5c1e06f3541ce9ffc</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SMALL OPERATORS&quot;" target="&quot;NUCLEUS HIVES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">14.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Small Operators occasionally produce nucleus hives with extra bees."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-c0a8c416dc0695d5c1e06f3541ce9ffc</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEEKEEPING EQUIPMENT DEALERS&quot;" target="&quot;PACKAGE BEES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">18.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Beekeeping Equipment Dealers advertise and supply package bees."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-c0a8c416dc0695d5c1e06f3541ce9ffc</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;OPTIMUM TIME FOR STARTING A COLONY&quot;" target="&quot;PLACING ORDERS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Optimum Time for Starting a Colony is the ideal period for placing orders and initiating beekeeping activities."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-c0a8c416dc0695d5c1e06f3541ce9ffc</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;LAST-MINUTE ORDERS&quot;" target="&quot;OPTIMUM TIME&quot;">
  <data key="d4">14.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Last-Minute Orders are placed very close to the Optimum Time, which may result in delays."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-c0a8c416dc0695d5c1e06f3541ce9ffc</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;TRUCKLOAD SHIPMENTS&quot;" target="&quot;PACKAGE BEES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">18.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Truckload Shipments deliver Package Bees in the spring."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-c0a8c416dc0695d5c1e06f3541ce9ffc</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;MAIL ORDER&quot;" target="&quot;PACKAGE BEES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">14.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Mail Order is another method for obtaining Package Bees, where orders are consolidated and shipped."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-c0a8c416dc0695d5c1e06f3541ce9ffc</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;OPTIMUM TIME&quot;" target="&quot;STARTING A COLONY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">18.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Optimum Time is the ideal period for Starting a Colony, typically early in the year."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-c0a8c416dc0695d5c1e06f3541ce9ffc</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;OPTIMUM TIME&quot;" target="&quot;RUSH&quot;">
  <data key="d4">14.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Rush is the increased demand and activity during the Optimum Time, which can lead to delays."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-c0a8c416dc0695d5c1e06f3541ce9ffc</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;RESERVATIONS&quot;" target="&quot;DISCUSSION&quot;">
  <data key="d4">12.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Discussions can help alleviate Reservations about dealing with bees."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-49ee09b3db57739dfa10e0ec383b5a4e</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;RESERVATIONS&quot;" target="&quot;WORK WITH BEES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Initial Reservations can be overcome by engaging in Work with Bees."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-49ee09b3db57739dfa10e0ec383b5a4e</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;RESERVATIONS&quot;" target="&quot;ANTHROPOMORPHISM&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Anthropomorphism can help explain and discuss bees, reducing initial Reservations."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-49ee09b3db57739dfa10e0ec383b5a4e</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;DISCUSSION&quot;" target="&quot;WORK WITH BEES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Discussions lead to practical Work with Bees, helping to understand and manage bees better."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-49ee09b3db57739dfa10e0ec383b5a4e</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;MEDICAL DEVICE&quot;" target="&quot;LAWS AND REGULATIONS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Laws and regulations govern the safety and effectiveness of medical devices."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-ffea4d43ecf72d0e1bf7106003d38157</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;GOVERNMENTAL ENTITIES&quot;" target="&quot;COMPANY AND ITS SUBSIDIARIES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">14.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Company and its Subsidiaries must also comply with regulations from other Governmental Entities that regulate the safety and effectiveness of medical devices and biological products."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-9125101d4917c40eb7ad06f5e3925ae7</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;GOVERNMENTAL ENTITIES&quot;" target="&quot;FDCA PERMITS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">9.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Governmental Entities issue FDCA Permits, which are necessary for the safe and effective distribution of medical devices and biological products."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-9125101d4917c40eb7ad06f5e3925ae7</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY AND ITS SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;FDA&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Company and its Subsidiaries must comply with FDA laws and regulations for the manufacture, testing, distribution, and marketing of medical devices and biological products."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-9125101d4917c40eb7ad06f5e3925ae7</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY AND ITS SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;MEDICAL DEVICES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">18.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Company and its Subsidiaries are responsible for ensuring that medical devices meet the necessary standards and regulations set by the FDA and other Governmental Entities."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-9125101d4917c40eb7ad06f5e3925ae7</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY AND ITS SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;FDCA PERMITS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">20.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Company and its Subsidiaries require specific FDCA Permits, such as 510(k)s and PMAs, to conduct business in the United States."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-9125101d4917c40eb7ad06f5e3925ae7</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY AND ITS SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;PRE-MARKET NOTIFICATIONS UNDER SECTION 510(K)&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Company and its Subsidiaries require pre-market notifications under section 510(k) for the manufacture, testing, distribution, and marketing of medical devices."</data>
