<edge source="&quot;C- _ABL_ GENE&quot;" target="&quot;PHILADELPHIA CHROMOSOME&quot;">
  <data key="d4">27.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"c- _abl_ gene is located on the Philadelphia chromosome, which is associated with CML."&lt;SEP&gt;"c- _abl_ gene is located on the Philadelphia chromosome."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-d0cf0b37864347226f145a22592586fb</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
