  <data key="d4">9.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The c- _src_ gene, found in normal cells, is involved in cellular regulation and was studied by Varmus and Bishop in relation to tumor viruses, highlighting its potential role in cellular processes and viral infection mechanisms."</data>
